{"tid":512550,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"未夠20歲就比班同學話我似TVB個夏雨,好撚灰!!","createTime":"2017-12-28T15:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T16:20:24.000Z","uid":139815,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5e89de3c121fff6d061ba1936365aa3dab900415","tid":512550,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"以前都好好地,前幾日學校聖誕聯歡會<br />\n班會活動玩爭凳仔,咁我份人一向work hard play hard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪好落力搶張凳囉,最後玩到得返3個人2張凳<br />\n<br />\n班上有個死mk,大大聲指住我話咩: 夏雨丫~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後有大半班男女同學都一齊笑,連老師都話我似佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現在班會群組,個個人叫我做正爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明明唔似佢,起碼我後生佢好多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但班仆街仔仆街女話我個髮型似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明我係碎剪短髮(日系路線)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟班上那些mk偽韓偽abc比清爽得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下星期返學,我唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好怕後生版夏雨呢個朵,會跟足我餘下既中學生涯,請問各位巴絲有咩方法令佢地唔再笑我似?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1a94bd402ded374f1a5b154edd0ca3b68f35d5","tid":512550,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"btw勿起底"},{"pid":"285e48b4d0cd7c3f72e3316427c77de314d57295","tid":512550,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36e972f8fc5c990ae83503c9eeace272e5070ed0","tid":512550,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"285e48b4d0cd7c3f72e3316427c77de314d57295","tid":512550,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"其實我好怕,佢地第日會玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n安排班上既豬西女同學做司棋姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41bc9e8ed6d66a66cb5183a1cd343135c3a12b85","tid":512550,"uid":36383,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/232150_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F232150_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ea579c7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97b3de50cf4c8cfc44cc5005776343cdddeda648","tid":512550,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41bc9e8ed6d66a66cb5183a1cd343135c3a12b85","tid":512550,"uid":36383,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/232150_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F232150_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ea579c7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"佢地話我似最新個版本,但明明我個髮型冇咁貼,係偷薄碎剪<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.tvb.com/ii/35/98993/000009899279_1511323411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.tvb.com%2Fii%2F35%2F98993%2F000009899279_1511323411.jpg&h=a270c1b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53f4b10dea02d9daa038c5e3f1d2a6560c8caf73","tid":512550,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"比負評我的人係咩心態?"},{"pid":"47faa762e29f8c3dc8f71afbb581a69260f4b62a","tid":512550,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97b3de50cf4c8cfc44cc5005776343cdddeda648","tid":512550,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"41bc9e8ed6d66